<div class="title">Easy Method for Consumption</div>
<div class="substance">Cacti - T. peruvianus</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Zae+Dawg&Exact=1">Zae Dawg</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Zae Dawg. "Easy Method for Consumption: An Experience with Cacti - T. peruvianus (exp44396)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 23, 2007. erowid.org/exp/44396</div>

